cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.parser.identifierstable.types.subroutine

Class SubroutineDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.parser.identifierstable.types.subroutine.SubroutineDescriptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypeDescriptor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FunctionDescriptor, ProcedureDescriptor

    public abstract class SubroutineDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object
implements TypeDescriptor
    Base type descriptor for subroutines. It contains the list of its formal parameters and an instance of PascalSubroutine representing the subroutine.
